    "en": {
      "title": "Blessings of the Maha Sangharatne to the Acting President",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "After taking the oath of office, Acting President Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe received the blessings of the Maha Sangharatne at Kollupitiya Valukarama.",
        "Kollupitiya Walukaramadhipati Maharagama Nanda Nahimi recited Seth Pirith and blessed the Acting President by placing the auspicious casket on his head.",
        "Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe was sworn in as the Acting President at Kollupitiya Walukarama."
      ],
      "title_ents": [
        {
          "text": "the Maha Sangharatne",
          "label": "PERSON"
        }
      ],
